Package org.bluezoo.gumdrop.mime

Class Parameter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bluezoo.gumdrop.mime.Parameter
  • public final class Parameter
extends java.lang.Object
    A parameter in a structured MIME header value such as Content-Type or Content-Disposition. It consists of a name and a value.
    Author:
    Chris Burdess

      • toHeaderValue

        public java.lang.String toHeaderValue()
        Serializes this parameter to RFC 2231 compliant header format.
        • ASCII token values: name=value
        • ASCII values with specials: name="value" with escaping
        • Non-ASCII values: name*=UTF-8''percent-encoded
        Returns:
        the serialized parameter suitable for inclusion in a header
        See Also:
        RFC 2231
